# Pod2Vid Environment Setup

## Required Environment Variables

### Hugging Face Token (Required for Speaker Diarization)
```bash
export HF_TOKEN="<your_huggingface_token_here>"
```

To get your token:
1. Visit: https://hf.co/settings/tokens
2. Create a new token
3. Accept model licenses:
   - https://hf.co/pyannote/segmentation
   - https://hf.co/pyannote/speaker-diarization

## Usage

### Local Development
```bash
export HF_TOKEN="<your_token>"
streamlit run app.py
```

### Cloud Deployment
Set `HF_TOKEN` in your cloud platform:
- **Streamlit Cloud**: Secrets management
- **Codespaces**: Repository secrets
- **Railway/Render**: Environment variables